title: Grateful Dead Live at Richfield Coliseum on 1991-09-06
description:
Set 1

Feel Like A Stranger, Bertha, Wang Dang Doodle, El Paso, Just Like Tom Thumb's Blues, It's All Over Now, Bird Song

Set 2

Victim Or The Crime-> Crazy Fingers-> Playin' In The Band-> Terrapin Station-> Drums-> Jam-> Dark Star Jam-> All Along The Watchtower-> Stella Blue-> Around & Around, E: Knockin' On Heaven's Door

reviews.review_text: Fantastic Show I was at this show, my friend and I both rate this as one of 3 best (we have seen about 48 shows overall since 1989) we ever experienced.
